Title: Prohibits the sale and possession of any part or product of a Giraffe
Summary: Prohibits the process, sale, offer for sale, purchase, trade, barter, distribution or possession of any part or product of the skin or body of a Giraffe.
LawCode: Add Art 11 Title 5 §11-0535-b, amd §71-0919, En Con L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the environmental conservation law, in relation to prohibiting the sale and possession of any part or product of a Giraffe
